<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="beyond-prep">beyond <strong><em>prep</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /bɪ'jɒnd/    美 /bɪ'jɑːnd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[表示位置] 在…的那边；远于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is the only place beyond the Earth to have been visited by humans.  
这是人类到过的地球以外的唯一地方。</p><footer>外研⑧ – 7</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[表示时间] 在…以后；迟于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The party went on until beyond midnight.
这次聚会一直持续到午夜以后。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[表示数量、水平、限度] 超出：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I spent my childhood working, with responsibilities beyond my age. 
我的童年是在工作中度过的，承担着与年龄不相符的责任。</p><footer>2010 重庆</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Any driver found drinking beyond the limit will be charged.  
任何司机如被发现饮酒超限都会被指控。</p><footer>2011 福建</footer></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>[表示范围] 超出…的范围；非…所及：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>beyond repair / control / belief</strong>
无法修理/控制/相信</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>beyond the reach of sb / beyond one’s reach</strong>
够不着；力所不及</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Such test is <strong>far beyond</strong> the ability of the average schoolkid. 
这样的测试远远超过了普通学童的能力。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.★ <strong>[常用于否定句和疑问句] 除…以外：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I know nothing of it beyond what he told me. 
除了他告诉我的以外，别的我什么都不知道。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-beyond-sb">be beyond sb</h3>
<p>1.<strong>超出某人的理解能力：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The whole problem was quite beyond him. 
他根本无法理解这个问题。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Everybody was touched <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (无以言表) after they heard her moving story.  （2009 全国改）  </li>
<li>Elizabeth has already achieved success <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ her wildest dreams.   （2008 陕西）<br />
A.at<br />
B.beyond<br />
C.within<br />
D.upon  </li>
<li>This new model of car is so expensive that it is <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (超出) the reach of those with average income.   </li>
<li>It’s quite <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (超出我的理解能力) why such things have been allowed to happen.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. beyond words  2. B  3. beyond  4. beyond me  </p></div>